10 REM ON EXPR GOTO/GOSUB DEMO -- O(1) DISPATCH
20 REM EMULATE A 4-OPCODE BYTECODE INTERPRETER USING ON .. GOSUB
30 LET A = 0
40 REM SCRIPT: 1=NOP, 2=PUSH-ONE, 3=DOUBLE, 4=PRINT
50 LET B = 2
60 GOSUB 1000
70 LET B = 2
80 GOSUB 1000
90 LET B = 3
100 GOSUB 1000
110 LET B = 4
120 GOSUB 1000
130 END
1000 REM DISPATCH: COLLAPSED FROM A 4-DEEP IF CHAIN
1010 ON B GOSUB 2000, 2100, 2200, 2300
1020 RETURN
2000 REM OP 1: NOP
2010 RETURN
2100 REM OP 2: PUSH ONE
2110 LET A = A + 1
2120 RETURN
2200 REM OP 3: DOUBLE
2210 LET A = A * 2
2220 RETURN
2300 REM OP 4: PRINT
2310 PRINT "A=";A
2320 RETURN
RUN
